본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap (modality-platform). hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 targeted protein degradation (TPD) — small-molecule-mediated targeted protein degradation paradigm 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 TPD modality 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_gene_therapy_platform` (vector + payload) + `.roadmap.disease_cell_therapy_platform` (engineered cell): protein degradation TPD = small-molecule-mediated targeted protein degradation — PROTAC + LYTAC + AUTAC + molecular glue + RIBOTAC + PHOTAC. 2018+ era. 양자-VQE 의 fit dense (E3 ligase + target binding + ternary complex modeling — 가장 challenging modeling problem 중 하나).)

scope:
