- E3 ligase 다양화 (CRBN + VHL + MDM2 + IAP + RNF114 + DCAF + cIAP)
- E3 substrate receptor 발견 + diversification
- pharmacology — sub-stoichiometric + catalytic + 약물 효율
- delivery 한정 + oral bioavailability + permeability + Lipinski rule of 5 외부
- 면역학 + 종양 + 신경 + 만성질환 적용
- ternary complex 안정성 + 양자-VQE leverage
