## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ARV-110 bavdegalutamide (Arvinas) 2019** = first-in-human PROTAC clinical entry — AR mCRPC. enzalutamide/abiraterone-resistant 환자. Phase 3 도달. PROTAC modality 의 임상 viable 첫 증명. quantum-VQE 의 ternary complex modeling fit 가장 challenging — E3 + target + linker geometry.
2. **Arvinas + Kymera + Nurix + Cullgen + Vividion + Foghorn + Frontier + Plexium + Dialectic + BeiGene + BMS-Celgene 등 14+ Phase 1-3** = TPD platform 임상 paradigm 본격화. ARV-471 vepdegestrant 2024 VERITAC-2 Phase 3 + KT-474 IRAK4 atopic dermatitis Phase 2 + NX-2127/NX-5948 BTK + BGB-16673 BTK + DT2216 BCL-XL + KT-333 STAT3 등 14+ active.
3. **양자-VQE ternary complex modeling 가장 challenging modeling problem 중 하나** = small molecule + E3 ligase + target protein 3-body + linker geometry + cooperativity (α factor) + neo-substrate evolution. classical docking 한계 + protein-protein interaction fit + induced fit cooperativity 가 quantum chemistry leverage point. 그러나 size 가 큰 system → fragmentation 필요.
4. **IMID 1990s historical molecular glue 첫 발견** = thalidomide 1957 birth defect → 1998 MM 재승인 → lenalidomide 2005 → pomalidomide 2013 → CRBN substrate receptor 발견 (2010 Handa) → IKZF1/3 ubiquitin substrate 발견 (2014 Lu/Krönke) — pre-PROTAC era 첫 mol glue. PROTAC 이전부터 임상 활용 + retroactive mechanism elucidation.
5. **LYTAC (Bertozzi 2020) + AUTAC (Sasaki 2019) + ATTEC (Lu 2019) 2019-2020 paradigm expansion** = ubiquitin-proteasome 외부 — extracellular protein (LYTAC ASGPR-mediated lysosome) + 자가소화작용 (AUTAC + ATTEC) + RNA (RIBOTAC) + photo-activation (PHOTAC). intracellular cytosolic-target only PROTAC paradigm 외부.
6. **Lipinski rule of 5 외부 + delivery + oral bioavailability + permeability 한정** = TPD 분자량 700-1500 Da 가 일반적 (PROTAC ARV-110 ~700 Da + ARV-471 ~620 Da + KT-474 ~700 Da). beyond rule of 5 (bRo5). 경구 흡수 + permeability + plasma protein binding + clearance — drug-like property optimization 가 임상 진입 여부 결정.
7. **molecular glue (mol glue) vs PROTAC paradigm distinction** = mol glue (단일 small molecule, 분자량 ~500 Da, IMID + GSPT1 + IKZF2 + WIZ + ARID1A 등) vs PROTAC (bivalent 분자량 700-1500 Da). mol glue 가 oral viable + drug-like property 우위 — 그러나 발견 challenge (induced PPI 새로 발견). DEL screening + computational prediction 가 mol glue discovery engine.
8. **VHL ligand vs CRBN ligand 2-3-fold 효능 차이 + neo-substrate evolution + ternary complex stabilization** = E3 ligase 선택 (CRBN vs VHL vs MDM2 vs IAP vs RNF114 vs DCAF) 가 효능 + selectivity 좌우. neo-substrate evolution = mol glue + PROTAC 가 새로운 ubiquitin substrate 유도 — IKZF1/3 IMID + GSPT1 CC-90009 + IKZF2 DKY709 + WIZ dWIZ-2 — substrate 다양화.
9. **K-pharma TPD — Oncocross + 한미 + GC + Daewoong + 동아 등 한국 TPD pipeline** = K-pharma TPD entry 시작 단계. Oncocross AI-driven TPD platform + 한미 next-gen PROTAC + GC PROTAC research. 글로벌 TPD pipeline 200+ 중 한국 비중 작음 — 그러나 catch-up window 있음.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음 + 양자-VQE in-silico-only** = TPD 임상 paradigm 본격화 (14+ Phase 1-3) — 그러나 hexa-bio quantum-only contribution 한정. ternary complex modeling 가장 challenging 인 만큼 in-silico leverage 가능 — 그러나 wet-lab 검증 없이 임상 의미 한정.

